         <p class="- topic/p ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">ERROR MESSAGE CONFIGURATOR</uicontrol> page, the error message that is currently displayed in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Value</uicontrol> field is <msgph class="+ topic/ph sw-d/msgph ">Invalid range. Min value should be lesser or equal to Max value.</msgph> This error message must be more descriptive and modified to <msgph class="+ topic/ph sw-d/msgph ">Invalid range. Value entered in "Min Risk Score" should be lesser or equal to value entered in the "Max Risk Score.</msgph>
